sputnikglobe.com/img/103189/89/1031898913_0:233:4455:2739_640x0_80_0_0_920738b5c75e998d9e1328a3e899c465.jpg 640w,https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/103189/89/1031898913_0:233:4455:2739_1280x0_80_0_0_40f4979a6372778d36c4b044ec76850f.jpg 1280w,https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/103189/89/1031898913_0:233:4455:2739_1920x0_80_0_0_69909e453dc7a63ba03f25e96ec699a6.jpg 1920w" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></div></div><div class="media__copyright " data-nosnippet=""><div class="media__copyright-item m-copyright"> © AP Photo / 马特·洛克</div></div></div></div><div class="article__messengers"><div class="flex-align_center"><span class="article__google-news__label"></span></div><div class="flex-align_center"></div><div class="article__telegram-news flex-align_center"><span class="article__google-news__label">订阅</span></div><div class="flex-align_center"><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://t.me/SputnikInt" title="国际的" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">国际的</a></div><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://telegram.me/sputniknewsindia" title="印度" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">印度</a></div><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://t.me/sputnik_africa" title="非洲" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">非洲</a></div></div></div><div class="article__announce-text">据莫斯科（人造卫星）网报道：俄罗斯主要调查机构周六宣布，对最近在伏尔加格勒焚烧穆斯林圣书《古兰经》的副本进行刑事调查，怀疑是在乌克兰策划的。 </div></div><div class="article__body"><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">调查委员会告诉卫星通讯社：“当地居民 Nikita Zhuravel 因涉嫌触犯俄罗斯刑法第 148 条第 2 款的罪行而被捕。”</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">在一名男子在伏尔加格勒一座清真寺前焚烧古兰经的视频被上传到网上后，俄罗斯调查人员展开了搜捕行动。如果罪名成立，朱拉维尔将面临最高三年的监禁，罪名是冒犯宗教感情。 </div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="quote"><div class="article__quote"><div class="article__quote-text">该委员会告诉人造卫星，嫌疑人已经承认从乌克兰特工那里收到了 10,000 卢布（125 美元）作为布置和拍摄古兰经焚烧的奖励。他还说他为乌克兰人制作了俄罗斯军事基地的视频。 </div><div class="article__quote-info"><div class="elem-info"><div class="elem-info__share"><div class="share" data-id="1110492121" data-url="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230520/russia-opens-criminal-probe-into-kiev-instigated-quran-burning-1110492121.html?share-block=1110492124" data-title="The committee told Sputnik that the suspect had confessed to receiving 10,000 rubles ($125) from Ukrainian agents as a reward for staging and filming the Quran burning. He also said he had made videos of Russian military sites for Ukrainians."></div></div></div></div></div></div></div> ]]>;</description><pubDate> Sat, 20 May 2023 21:02:02 GMT</pubDate><guid ispermalink="false"> https://sputniknews.com/20230520/russia-opens-criminal-probe-into-kiev-instigated-quran-burning-1110492121.html</guid><link/> https://sputniknews.com/20230520/russia-opens-criminal-probe-into-kiev-instigated-quran-burning-1110492121.html<category>俄罗斯</category><category>调查</category><category>俄罗斯调查委员会</category><category>古兰经</category><category>伊斯兰教</category><category>伏尔加格勒</category><category>乌克兰危机</category></item><item><title><![CDATA[Durham Report: Is Reckoning Coming for Clintons and Bidens?]]></title><description><![CDATA[<div class="article__header"><div class="article__announce"><div class="media" data-media-tipe="ar16x9"><div class="media__size"><div class="photoview__open" data-photoview-group="1110490817" data-photoview-src="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/107851/17/1078511724_0:0:3071:2048_1440x900_80_0_1_780e39bf99587cd9a0dca8494de4280d.jpg?source-sid=ap_photo" data-photoview-image-id="1078511722" data-photoview-sharelink="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230520/durham-report-is-reckoning-coming-for-clintons-and-bidens-1110490817.html?share-img=1078511722"><noindex><div class="photoview__open-info"> <span class="photoview__copyright">© AP Photo / Evan Vucci</span><span class="photoview__desc-text">副总统乔·拜登（左）与前国务卿希拉里·克林顿在 12 月 8 日星期四于国会山举行的参议院少数党领袖哈里·里德肖像揭幕仪式上与前国务卿希拉里·克林顿一起大笑。 2016 年，华盛顿。</span> </div></noindex><img media-type="ar16x9" data-source-sid="ap_photo" alt="Vice President Joe Biden, left, laughs with former Secretary of State Hillary Clinton during a ceremony to unveil a portrait of Senate Minority Leader Harry Reid, D-Nev., on Capitol Hill, Thursday, Dec. 8, 2016, in Washington. - Sputnik International, 1920, 20.05.2023" title="2016 年 12 月 8 日星期四，在华盛顿举行的参议院少数党领袖哈里·里德肖像揭幕仪式上，副总统乔·拜登（左）与前国务卿希拉里·克林顿一起大笑。" src="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/107851/17/1078511724_0:161:3071:1888_1920x0_80_0_0_3033426f462bb53b03d71625ff188443.jpg" decoding="async" width="1920" height="1080" srcset="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/107851/17/1078511724_0:161:3071:1888_640x0_80_0_0_af6b1702ac8706bd2e380fea981c7cac.jpg 640w,https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/107851/17/1078511724_0:161:3071:1888_1280x0_80_0_0_d98d07670f5f22582c75c607860c8e28.jpg 1280w,https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/107851/17/1078511724_0:161:3071:1888_1920x0_80_0_0_3033426f462bb53b03d71625ff188443.jpg 1920w" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></div></div><div class="media__copyright " data-nosnippet=""><div class="media__copyright-item m-copyright"> © 美联社照片 / Evan Vucci </div></div></div></div><div class="article__messengers"><div class="flex-align_center"><span class="article__google-news__label"></span></div><div class="flex-align_center"></div><div class="article__telegram-news flex-align_center"><span class="article__google-news__label">订阅</span></div><div class="flex-align_center"><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://t.me/SputnikInt" title="国际的" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">国际的</a></div><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://telegram.me/sputniknewsindia" title="印度" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">印度</a></div><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://t.me/sputnik_africa" title="非洲" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">非洲</a></div></div></div><div class="article__author"><div class="article__author-item"><div class="article__author-wrapper"><div class="article__author-info"><div class="article__author-name">叶卡捷琳娜布林诺娃</div><div class="article__author-links"><a class="m-color-main" href="https://sputniknews.com/author_ekaterina_blinova/" title="所有材料">所有材料</a> <a data-modal-open="feedback_author" href="mailto:e.blinova@sputniknews.com" title="写给作者">写给作者</a></div></div></div></div></div><div class="article__announce-text">特别顾问约翰达勒姆关于特朗普 - 俄罗斯调查的报告产生了意想不到的副作用：众议院共和党立法者现在呼吁联邦调查局重新开始对克林顿基金会的调查。 Sputnik 与华尔街分析师 Charles Ortel 讨论了这一发展。 </div></div><div class="article__body"><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text"> “人们希望约翰·达勒姆分享的内容绰绰有余，以促使人们更严格地了解克林顿基金会丑闻的广泛范围，这些丑闻首先由调查记者报道，包括约翰·所罗门和彼得·施韦泽，他们实际上应该获得普利策奖，”查尔斯·奥特尔说，他是几年来一直在对克林顿夫妇的慈善网络进行私人调查。 “ <a href="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230216/why-elon-musk-would-have-made-great-special-counsel--independent-journos-do-better-job-than-doj-1107514193.html" target="_blank">主流媒体‘调查员’</a>对试图理解为什么奥巴马政府中有如此多的人参与了令人发指的行为，而这些行为随后被高层政府官员及其在许多官僚机构的同谋所掩盖，对此表现出不小的兴趣。”</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">尽管<a href="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230516/durham-report-what-is-known-so-far-1110402005.html" target="_blank">约翰·达勒姆 (John Durham) 被指派调查</a>联邦调查局 (FBI) 交叉火力飓风调查的起源，目的是挖掘唐纳德·特朗普竞选活动涉嫌与俄罗斯的关系，但特别检察官也揭示了强大的民主党参与者，包括前总统候选人希拉里·克林顿 (Hillary Clinton) <a href="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230209/whos-jake-sullivan-the-man-who-reportedly-assembled-dream-team-to-destroy-nord-stream-1107273707.html" target="_blank">及其随行人员</a>.达勒姆冗长的法庭动议暴露了克林顿竞选团队在兜售将他与俄罗斯阿尔法银行和克里姆林宫联系起来的反特朗普恶作剧中的作用。早在 2018 年，特别顾问罗伯特·穆勒 (Robert Mueller) 就得出结论，认为特朗普与俄罗斯的故事没有证据依据。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">此外，达勒姆提请注意这样一个事实，即联邦调查局<a href="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230515/us-special-counsel-probe-finds-fbis-handling-of-trump-russia-probe-seriously-deficient-1110387179.html" target="_blank">在以可疑借口匆忙调查特朗普的</a>同时，对唐纳德的总统竞争对手希拉里克林顿进行了至少四次调查。 2016 年初，联邦调查局在阿肯色州、纽约和哥伦比亚特区的外地办事处启动了上述三项针对克林顿基金会的“可能犯罪活动”的调查。另一项调查早在 2014 年就开始了，原因是有人声称外国政府试图向克林顿夫妇的慈善机构非法捐款，以讨好希拉里担任国务卿期间的好感。令人费解的是，该局的所有四项调查都在 2016 年选举之前被关闭。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="h3"><h3 class="article__h2">美国联邦机构此前多次未能调查克林顿慈善机构</h3></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">Ortel 强调说，克林顿基金会很早就进入了美国联邦当局的视线。尽管如此，据他说，每次调查人员都未能完成他们的调查并发现明显的不一致和明显的欺诈行为。 </div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="quote"><div class="article__quote"><div class="article__quote-text"> “公开的记录显示，从 2001 年 2 月到 2005 年初，詹姆斯·康梅、罗伯特·穆勒、美国国税局和其他人首先调查了最初的克林顿基金会，调查人员‘遗漏’了明显的欺诈行为。起初，这令人惊讶，因为调查人员应该能够看到，在 2001 年至 2004 年的关键时期，克林顿基金会从未对财务报表进行必要的审计，当时阿肯色州小石城总统中心得到资助和建设，”这位华尔街分析师说。 </div><div class="article__quote-info"><div class="elem-info"><div class="elem-info__share"><div class="share" data-id="1110490817" data-url="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230520/durham-report-is-reckoning-coming-for-clintons-and-bidens-1110490817.html?share-block=1110491947" data-title="&quot;Publicly available records show that the original Clinton Foundation was first investigated by James Comey, Robert Mueller, the IRS, and others from February 2001 through early 2005 and that the investigators 'missed' obvious frauds. This is surprising, at first, in that investigators should have been able to see that the Clinton Foundation never produced required audits of financial statements in the crucial period from 2001 through 2004, when the Little Rock, Arkansas Presidential Center was financed and constructed,&quot; said the Wall Street analyst."></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text"> “公共记录还显示，克林顿基金会从未在 1997 年 10 月 23 日至 1997 年 12 月 31 日这一关键的‘短期’期间提交必要的国税局报告，当时本应为克林顿第二届就职委员会筹集的剩余资金被捐赠给克林顿基金会。基金会。在 2005 年 4 月 25 日之后，我的评估是威廉·克林顿总统基金会不再是一种可行的免税实体形式，被称为“公共慈善机构”，因为它未能完全修改其公司章程和章程，并且此外，在比尔·克林顿的直接监督下，最初的克林顿基金会于 2001 年夏天开始筹集资金并从事从未被美国国税局有效授权为免税的活动，当时它使用纽约的办事处城市没有遵守严格的州和城市慈善法，”Ortel 继续说道。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">根据这位华尔街分析师的说法，克林顿基金会从 2003 年 12 月 31 日开始对财务报表进行了“明显有缺陷的审计”，并最终在美国境内外“虚假借口”筹集了数十亿美元。 </div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="quote"><div class="article__quote"><div class="article__quote-text"> “许多外国政府和许多富有的捐助者已经向克林顿基金会及其所谓的附属机构提供了数十亿美元的捐款，似乎没有注意到这些实体并没有正式存在或没有适当地报告他们的活动，”他继续说道。 “这种众所周知的公共记录没有充分的理由，也没有充分的理由相信捐助者寻求并可能从克林顿家族及其盟友那里获得的利益价值是他们对克林顿基金会捐款价值的许多倍。” </div><div class="article__quote-info"><div class="elem-info"><div class="elem-info__share"><div class="share" data-id="1110490817" data-url="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230520/durham-report-is-reckoning-coming-for-clintons-and-bidens-1110490817.html?share-block=1110491949" data-title="&quot;Many foreign governments and many rich contributors have sent, all together, billions of dollars in contributions towards the Clinton Foundation and its supposed affiliates without, seemingly, noticing that these entities did not formally exist or properly report concerning their activities,&quot; he continued. &quot;There is no good reason for this known public record and every reason to believe that donors sought and likely received benefits from the Clinton family and their allies worth many times the value of their contributions to the Clinton Foundation.&quot;"></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">他怀疑奥巴马政府很清楚克林顿夫妇明显的违规行为，但为了将希拉里克林顿推上美国国务卿的位置而掩盖了这些行为。因此，按照奥特尔的说法，美国国税局、司法部和其他机构对克林顿基金会的“违规行为”视而不见。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">为什么特别顾问约翰·达勒姆 (John Durham) 不深入研究联邦当局对克林顿基金会案件的处理方式？ “最有可能的是，约翰·达勒姆 (John Durham) 无权追溯至 1997 年 10 月 23 日，”这位华尔街分析师推测道。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="h3"><h3 class="article__h2">克林顿夫妇和拜登夫妇对待儿童手套都一视同仁</h3></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text"><a href="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230207/bans-bucks--bureaucracy-twitter-files-co-author-taibbi-on-big-techs-collusion-with-feds-1107047111.html" target="_blank">埃隆·马斯克 (Elon Musk) 的 Twitter 文件</a>显示，美国联邦调查局 (FBI) 决定停止对强大的克林顿王朝家族展开调查，这似乎与美国情报界在 2020 年压制亨特·拜登 (Hunter Biden) “来自地狱的笔记本电脑”故事惊人地相似。此外，正如众议院立法者最近透露的那样，多达<a href="https://sputnikglobe.com/20220526/if-hunters-laptop-from-hell-is-100-authentic-will-dirty-51-ex-spooks-be-held-accountable-1095806921.html" target="_blank">51 名前高级情报官员</a>迅速将《纽约邮报》投下的笔记本电脑重磅炸弹错误地贴上了“俄罗斯虚假信息”的标签，应当时的乔·拜登竞选活动特工安东尼·布林肯的要求。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">本月早些时候，众议院监督委员会主席詹姆斯·科默表示， <a href="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230511/fbi-refuses-republican-request-for-docs-tied-to-alleged-biden-criminal-scheme-1110250541.html" target="_blank">联邦调查局拒绝了众议院小组要求提供一份文件的请求</a>，该文件据称详细说明了<a href="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230510/memo-biden-family-received-millions-from-foreigners-when-joe-was-vp-1110242908.html" target="_blank">乔·拜登总统参与</a>一项与外国人的非法计划。 “从联邦调查局的回应中可以清楚地看出，监督委员会传唤的非机密记录是存在的，但他们拒绝将其提供给委员会。我们已经要求联邦调查局不仅提供这份记录，还要告知我们它对我们做了什么调查这些指控。联邦调查局未能做到这两点，”科默在 5 月 10 日宣布。 </div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="quote"><div class="article__quote"><div class="article__quote-text"> Ortel 说：“FBI 控制着颁发安全许可的过程，并且通过这个过程可能会了解很多关于联邦政府官员的信息。” “这项职能必须与其他调查活动完全分开，我怀疑它多年来一直没有分开。我们如何解释詹姆斯康梅在 2017 年 1 月 20 日之前吹嘘与当选总统特朗普对抗时表现出的神经？就职典礼和他从那时到现在的行为？如果联邦调查局在安全审查方面进展缓慢，那么它可能会阻碍即将上任的政府，就像特朗普政府所做的那样。” </div><div class="article__quote-info"><div class="elem-info"><div class="elem-info__share"><div class="share" data-id="1110490817" data-url="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230520/durham-report-is-reckoning-coming-for-clintons-and-bidens-1110490817.html?share-block=1110491950" data-title="&quot;The FBI controls the process of issuing security clearances and through this process likely learns much about many officials in the federal government,&quot; said Ortel. &quot;This function must be kept wholly separate from other investigative activities and I suspect it has not been kept separate for many years. How else do we explain the nerve exhibited by James Comey in bragging about confronting President-elect Trump before the January 20, 2017 Inauguration and his behavior from then to the present day? If the FBI slow-walks security reviews, it can then hobble the incoming administration, as it did in the case of the Trump administration.&quot;"></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="h3"><h3 class="article__h2">是时候调查深州腐败了</h3></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">在达勒姆报告发布后，现任和前任美国立法者呼吁重新开始对克林顿基金会的调查。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">众议院司法委员会联邦政府武器化小组委员会成员、佛罗里达州共和党众议员马特·盖茨 (Matt Gaetz) 表示：“克林顿夫妇在联邦调查局有一组人对他们进行干预，以避免追究刑事责任。这些问题绝对值得进一步曝光和审查。”每日邮报。 </div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="quote"><div class="article__quote"><div class="article__quote-text"> “绝对应该重新审视这些调查。国会没有理由不能与追查克林顿基金会的现场特工举行一系列听证会，并对他们进行公开采访。这些问题绝对值得额外曝光和审查，”呼应前共和党国会议员和前众议院监督委员会主席贾森查菲茨。 </div><div class="article__quote-info"><div class="elem-info"><div class="elem-info__share"><div class="share" data-id="1110490817" data-url="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230520/durham-report-is-reckoning-coming-for-clintons-and-bidens-1110490817.html?share-block=1110491952" data-title="&quot;Absolutely these investigations should be revisited. There's no reason why Congress can't have a series of hearings with the field agents who were pursuing the Clinton Foundation, and public interviews with them as well. These matters absolutely warrant additional exposure and review,&quot; echoed former Republican congressman and ex-House Oversight Committee chair Jason Chaffetz."></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text"> Charles Ortel 表示希望达勒姆报告将引发“深入研究免税组织的活动，特别是当这些组织在国外运作和/或涉及政治家庭时。” </div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="quote"><div class="article__quote"><div class="article__quote-text"> “对所谓的免税组织的非法活动和腐败监督的真正调查应该是一个紧迫的、两党的优先事项，特别是在美国正在努力支付账单、减少我们的年度政府赤字和管理我们巨额债务的当下， ”华尔街分析师总结道。 </div><div class="article__quote-info"><div class="elem-info"><div class="elem-info__share"><div class="share" data-id="1110490817" data-url="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230520/durham-report-is-reckoning-coming-for-clintons-and-bidens-1110490817.html?share-block=1110491953" data-title="&quot;Real investigations of illegal activities and of corrupt oversight of supposed tax-exempt organizations should be an urgent, bi-partisan priority particularly in the present moment when America is struggling to pay its bills, reduce our annual government deficits and manage our towering debts,&quot; the Wall Street analyst concluded."></div></div></div></div></div></div></div> ]]>;</description><pubDate> Sat, 20 May 2023 19:10:24 GMT</pubDate><guid ispermalink="false"> https://sputniknews.com/20230520/durham-report-is-reckoning-coming-for-clintons-and-bidens-1110490817.html</guid><link/> https://sputniknews.com/20230520/durham-report-is-reckoning-coming-for-clintons-and-bidens-1110490817.html<category>美洲</category><category>我们</category><category>希拉里·克林顿</category><category>比尔·克林顿</category><category>查尔斯奥特尔</category><category>联邦调查局</category><category>克林顿基金会</category><category>共和党人</category><category>达勒姆报告</category><category>约翰达勒姆</category><category>唐纳德·特朗普</category><category>亨特·拜登</category><category>中央情报局 (CIA)</category><category>笔记本电脑</category><category>付费玩</category><category>调查</category></item><item><title><![CDATA[Pledge of NATO Membership for Kiev Would Confirm Russia’s Warnings About Bloc’s Aggressive Posture]]></title><description><![CDATA[<div class="article__header"><div class="article__announce"><div class="media" data-media-tipe="ar16x9"><div class="media__size"><div class="photoview__open" data-photoview-group="1110490624" data-photoview-src="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e5/0c/10/1091567690_0:0:3076:2047_1440x900_80_0_1_17b4f2e147f9a6c4ac71b49ed160c08f.jpg?source-sid=" data-photoview-image-id="1091567686" data-photoview-sharelink="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230520/pledge-of-nato-membership-for-kiev-would-confirm-russias-warnings-about-blocs-aggressive-posture-1110490624.html?share-img=1091567686"><noindex><div class="photoview__open-info"> <span class="photoview__copyright">© Sergei SUPINSKY</span> <span class="photoview__desc-text">2019 年 10 月 31 日，乌克兰总统泽伦斯基和北约秘书长延斯·斯托尔滕贝格在基辅会面后举行联合新闻发布会</span></div></noindex><img media-type="ar16x9" data-source-sid="" alt="Ukrainian President Volodymyr Zelensky and NATO Secretary General Jens Stoltenberg hold a joint press conference following a meeting in Kiev on October 31, 2019 - Sputnik International, 1920, 20.05.2023" title="2019 年 10 月 31 日，乌克兰总统泽伦斯基和北约秘书长延斯·斯托尔滕贝格在基辅会面后举行联合新闻发布会" src="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e5/0c/10/1091567690_0:317:3076:2047_1920x0_80_0_0_b97764c87e048874ee353d3715cf0168.jpg" decoding="async" width="1920" height="1080" srcset="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e5/0c/10/1091567690_0:317:3076:2047_640x0_80_0_0_f7fb1d367ab52b4a22c915784e41a911.jpg 640w,https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e5/0c/10/1091567690_0:317:3076:2047_1280x0_80_0_0_c69661b3bde6f6290ff807f6493fd343.jpg 1280w,https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e5/0c/10/1091567690_0:317:3076:2047_1920x0_80_0_0_b97764c87e048874ee353d3715cf0168.jpg 1920w" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></div></div><div class="media__copyright " data-nosnippet=""><div class="media__copyright-item m-copyright"> © 谢尔盖·苏宾斯基</div></div></div></div><div class="article__messengers"><div class="flex-align_center"><span class="article__google-news__label"></span></div><div class="flex-align_center"></div><div class="article__telegram-news flex-align_center"><span class="article__google-news__label">订阅</span></div><div class="flex-align_center"><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://t.me/SputnikInt" title="国际的" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">国际的</a></div><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://telegram.me/sputniknewsindia" title="印度" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">印度</a></div><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://t.me/sputnik_africa" title="非洲" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">非洲</a></div></div></div><div class="article__author"><div class="article__author-item"><div class="article__author-wrapper"><div class="article__author-info"><div class="article__author-name">伊利亚楚卡诺夫</div><div class="article__author-links"> <a class="m-color-main" href="https://sputniknews.com/author_tsukanov_ilya/" title="所有材料">所有材料</a> <a data-modal-open="feedback_author" href="mailto:i.tsukanov@sputniknews.com" title="写给作者">写给作者</a></div></div></div></div></div><div class="article__announce-text">自 2008 年在布加勒斯特举行的北约峰会以来，两个主要政党的美国官员一直在讨论乌克兰加入西方联盟的问题，这可能成为该军事集团数十年来积极向东扩张的顶点。这也是北约与俄罗斯在乌克兰进行代理人战争的主要原因之一。 </div></div><div class="article__body"><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">在联盟即将举行的维尔纽斯峰会上给予基辅关于未来北约成员资格的任何形式的承诺将是一个糟糕的主意，这会破坏乌克兰的安全并导致莫斯科加倍开展其特别军事行动，大西洋理事会高级研究员约翰·R·德尼* ，总部位于华盛顿的顶级<a href="https://asiatimes.com/2022/06/neocon-think-tanks-are-driving-bidens-ukraine-policy/" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener">新保守主义</a>智囊团建议。 </div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="quote"><div class="article__quote"><div class="article__quote-text"><p>在最近为一家主要国际事务杂志<a href="https://foreignpolicy.com/2023/05/19/ukraine-nato-vilnius-zelensky-russia-summit/?tpcc=recirc_latest062921" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener">发表的一篇专栏文章</a>中，同时也是美国陆军战争学院战略研究所教授的德尼警告说，“为乌克兰加入北约铺平道路”几乎肯定会“恶化乌克兰在短期”，延长和升级危机。 </p></div><div class="article__quote-info"><div class="elem-info"><div class="elem-info__share"><div class="share" data-id="1110490624" data-url="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230520/pledge-of-nato-membership-for-kiev-would-confirm-russias-warnings-about-blocs-aggressive-posture-1110490624.html?share-block=1110490626" data-title="In a recent op-ed for a major international affairs magazine, Deni, who is also a professor at the US Army War College’s Strategic Studies Institute, warned that ‘laying a path for Ukrainian membership in NATO’ would almost certainly “worsen Ukraine’s security in the short run,” prolonging and escalating the crisis."></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">这样做还会违反该联盟长期以来的成员规则——该规则要求候选国之间不存在未解决的内部冲突或与邻国的边界争端。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">德尼写道，加入成员国的承诺也将有助于“发挥”莫斯科关于该联盟利用乌克兰作为进一步侵略俄罗斯的起点的非常公开的警告，同时不诚实地将俄罗斯的这些担忧称为“普京的错误信息运动”。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text"> “让乌克兰走上更快、更清晰的加入北约的道路，将普京的宣传变成了预言，”这位观察员建议道，但没有详细说明北约两年半的扩张和<a href="https://mid.ru/ru/foreign_policy/rso/nato/1790818/?lang=en" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener">俄罗斯拒绝两项全面的安全条约提案是如何</a>做到的于 2021 年底提出，这将有助于乌克兰保持中立，这构成了“宣传”。 </div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="quote"><div class="article__quote"><div class="article__quote-text"><p>德尼表示，乌克兰在加入北约方面“在政治上还没有做好准备”，因为该国未能达到该联盟自称的自由民主标准，尤其是在过去一年观察到“对公民自由的镇压”之后。 </p></div><div class="article__quote-info"><div class="elem-info"><div class="elem-info__share"><div class="share" data-id="1110490624" data-url="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230520/pledge-of-nato-membership-for-kiev-would-confirm-russias-warnings-about-blocs-aggressive-posture-1110490624.html?share-block=1110490630" data-title="Ukraine is also “not ready politically” for NATO membership, according to Deni, with the country failing to meet the alliance’s self-proclaimed liberal democratic standards, particularly following the “crackdown on civil liberties” observed over the past year."></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">北约不应向基辅提供如此正式的承诺，而应“关注盟友——尤其是欧洲盟友”如何“显着增加西方及其盟国先进军事平台的生产、交付和培训”，以对抗俄罗斯智库研究员认为，人力物力方面的优势。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">德尼的建议是新颖的，因为它来自华盛顿的顶级国际事务智囊团之一，其政策建议首先帮助引发了乌克兰危机。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">美国政界的反战声音提出了他们自己拒绝乌克兰加入北约的理由，理由包括危机<a href="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230515/ukraines-fanatical-ex-envoy-to-germany-parachutes-into-brazil-to-wreak-havoc-1110385455.html" target="_blank">升级为全球热核战争的风险等。</a>本周在接受波兰媒体采访时，资深美国经济学家和公共政策分析师杰弗里萨克斯<a href="https://myslpolska.info/2023/05/19/jeffrey-sachs-usa-udaja-ze-rzadza-swiatem/" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener">表示</a>，华盛顿“傲慢”地拒绝考虑俄罗斯的国家安全利益和解决莫斯科对北约扩张的担忧是目前冲突的主要原因，其中乌克兰部队正在使用西方提供的武器与俄罗斯作战。 </div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="quote"><div class="article__quote"><div class="article__quote-text"> “俄罗斯永远不会接受乌克兰加入北约。它要么在战场上击败乌克兰，要么继续一场漫长而令人筋疲力尽的战争，”萨克斯警告说。 “总的来说，乌克兰加入北约没有现实的途径，”这位学者强调。 </div><div class="article__quote-info"><div class="elem-info"><div class="elem-info__share"><div class="share" data-id="1110490624" data-url="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230520/pledge-of-nato-membership-for-kiev-would-confirm-russias-warnings-about-blocs-aggressive-posture-1110490624.html?share-block=1110490635" data-title="“Russia will never accept Ukrainian membership in NATO. It will either defeat Ukraine on the battlefield or continue a long, exhausting war,” Sachs warned. “Overall, there is no realistic path to Ukraine’s membership in NATO,” the academic stressed."></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">上周，著名国际关系学者约瑟夫·M·锡拉库扎博士<a href="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230514/tallinn-security-conference-pours-gasoline-on-fire-of-russia-nato-proxy-war-in-ukraine-1110355015.html" target="_blank">告诉人造卫星网</a>，北约安全机构计划在不考虑俄罗斯利益的情况下继续扩大联盟。锡拉库萨说，当前的危机是由外交失败造成的，并且由于西方政策精英对基辅有能力打败俄罗斯的“错觉”期望而继续存在。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">从总统普京到外交部长谢尔盖拉夫罗夫的俄罗斯高级官员一再警告说，乌克兰加入北约是一条明亮的“红线”，俄罗斯永远不会接受被越过。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text"> 2021 年底，在俄罗斯的安全提案公布后，普京与华盛顿和布鲁塞尔进行了一系列来回的外交沟通，坦率地说，乌克兰的红线是他们没有任何战略回旋余地俄罗斯。北约将“在乌克兰部署导弹系统，飞行 4-5 分钟即可到达莫斯科……他们只是把我们逼到了这样一种状态，我们不得不告诉他们：停下来，”普京当时<a href="https://sputnikglobe.com/20211226/putin-on-red-lines-west-has-pinned-russia-into-a-position-where-it-has-nowhere-to-fall-back-to-1091813306.html" target="_blank">说</a>。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text"> <em>* 被俄罗斯总检察长办公室列为不良实体。</em></div></div></div> ]]>;</description><pubDate> Sat, 20 May 2023 18:57:03 GMT</pubDate><guid ispermalink="false"> https://sputniknews.com/20230520/pledge-of-nato-membership-for-kiev-would-confirm-russias-warnings-about-blocs-aggressive-posture-1110490624.html</guid><link/> https://sputniknews.com/20230520/pledge-of-nato-membership-for-kiev-would-confirm-russias-warnings-about-blocs-aggressive-posture-1110490624.html<category>军队</category><category>弗拉基米尔普京</category><category>乌克兰</category><category>俄罗斯</category><category>北约</category><category>大西洋理事会</category><category>我们</category><category>扩张</category><category>北约东扩</category></item><item><title><![CDATA[Quad Leaders Pledge to Roll Out Open Radio Network in Pacific Region]]></title><description><![CDATA[<div class="article__header"><div class="article__announce"><div class="media" data-media-tipe="ar16x9"><div class="media__size"><div class="photoview__open" data-photoview-group="1110491516" data-photoview-src="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/105441/80/1054418069_0:0:2998:2481_1440x900_80_0_1_315eca1cae5da2320f4dabad6dbb046f.jpg?source-sid=ap_photo" data-photoview-image-id="1054418068" data-photoview-sharelink="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230520/quad-leaders-pledge-to-roll-out-open-radio-network-in-pacific-region-1110491516.html?share-img=1054418068"><noindex><div class="photoview__open-info"> <span class="photoview__copyright">© AP Photo / file /</span><span class="photoview__desc-text">射电望远镜位于加利福尼亚州莫哈韦沙漠的戈德斯通跟踪站</span></div></noindex><img media-type="ar16x9" data-source-sid="ap_photo" alt="Radio telescope located at the Goldstone Tracking Station in the Mojave Desert, California - Sputnik International, 1920, 20.05.2023" title="位于加利福尼亚州莫哈韦沙漠戈德斯通跟踪站的射电望远镜" src="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/105441/80/1054418069_0:398:2998:2084_1920x0_80_0_0_6cf5fc94429e10f97861544f69c1cb0a.jpg" decoding="async" width="1920" height="1080" srcset="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/105441/80/1054418069_0:398:2998:2084_640x0_80_0_0_655b953fc7fbf00d7e5fb899e4e37582.jpg 640w,https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/105441/80/1054418069_0:398:2998:2084_1280x0_80_0_0_91b63f4192fa41dbc02f61e4debae0fc.jpg 1280w,https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/105441/80/1054418069_0:398:2998:2084_1920x0_80_0_0_6cf5fc94429e10f97861544f69c1cb0a.jpg 1920w" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></div></div><div class="media__copyright " data-nosnippet=""><div class="media__copyright-item m-copyright"> ©美联社照片/文件/ </div></div></div></div><div class="article__messengers"><div class="flex-align_center"><span class="article__google-news__label"></span></div><div class="flex-align_center"></div><div class="article__telegram-news flex-align_center"><span class="article__google-news__label">订阅</span></div><div class="flex-align_center"><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://t.me/SputnikInt" title="国际的" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">国际的</a></div><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://telegram.me/sputniknewsindia" title="印度" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">印度</a></div><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://t.me/sputnik_africa" title="非洲" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">非洲</a></div></div></div><div class="article__announce-text">据莫斯科（人造卫星）网报道：澳大利亚、印度、日本和美国的领导人周六宣布，他们的国家将与太平洋群岛国家帕劳一道，在印太地区推出一个开放的无线电网络，以确保发展中经济体&#39;进入电信市场。 </div></div><div class="article__body"><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text"> “今天，我们宣布与帕劳合作部署太平洋地区首个开放无线电接入网络 (Open RAN)。Quad 致力于确保区域国家不会随着电信市场和网络架构的发展而落后，”他们的联合声明宣读。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text"> <a href="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230303/quad-countries-oppose-any-unilateral-actions-in-south-east-china-seas-1107988139.html" target="_blank">四人表示，</a>他们支持获得创新，这些创新将使各国有更多的供应商选择，以扩大其电信网络并使其现代化。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text"> Quad 的第三次面对面<a href="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230517/quad-leaders-to-meet-at-g7-after-biden-nixes-summit-to-handle-debt-ceiling-talks-1110426242.html" target="_blank">峰会于周六在日本广岛举行的 G7 峰会期间举行</a>。它汇集了澳大利亚总理安东尼·艾博年、印度总理纳伦德拉·莫迪、日本首相岸田文雄和美国总统乔·拜登。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">另外，四方要求缅甸和朝鲜进行建设性对话。他们呼吁缅甸执政军方释放所有被认为被任意拘留的人，并允许向包容性民主过渡，同时要求朝鲜停止发射弹道导弹并放弃追求核武器。</div></div></div> ]]>;</description><pubDate> Sat, 20 May 2023 18:54:24 GMT</pubDate><guid ispermalink="false"> https://sputniknews.com/20230520/quad-leaders-pledge-to-roll-out-open-radio-network-in-pacific-region-1110491516.html</guid><link/> https://sputniknews.com/20230520/quad-leaders-pledge-to-roll-out-open-radio-network-in-pacific-region-1110491516.html<category>军队</category><category>安东尼艾博年</category><category>四方安全对话 (QUAD)</category><category>澳大利亚</category><category>印度</category><category>日本</category><category>我们</category><category>印太</category></item><item><title><![CDATA[Stealthy Chinese Hypersonic Spy Drone Purportedly Spotted in Satellite Snap]]></title><description><![CDATA[<div class="article__header"><div class="article__announce"><div class="media" data-media-tipe="ar16x9"><div class="media__size"><div class="photoview__open" data-photoview-group="1110489362" data-photoview-src="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e7/05/14/1110489963_0:0:1200:806_1440x900_80_0_1_96dd27a6db7f925ac5cacafbbc71dedd.jpg?source-sid=not_sputnik_photo" data-photoview-image-id="1110489945" data-photoview-sharelink="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230520/stealthy-chinese-hypersonic-spy-drone-purportedly-spotted-in-satellite-snap-1110489362.html?share-img=1110489945"><noindex><div class="photoview__open-info"> <span class="photoview__copyright">© Photo : Twitter / @TheBaseLeg</span> <span class="photoview__desc-text">Planet Labs 卫星快照展示了美国认为的中国 WZ-8 高超音速侦察无人机。</span> </div></noindex><img media-type="ar16x9" data-source-sid="not_sputnik_photo" alt="Planet Labs satellite snap featuring what US believes is a Chinese WZ-8 hypersonic reconnaissance UAV. - Sputnik International, 1920, 20.05.2023" title="Planet Labs 卫星快照展示了美国认为的中国 WZ-8 高超音速侦察无人机。" src="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e7/05/14/1110489963_0:66:1201:741_1920x0_80_0_0_d30b3fa9dd0bfe34908ce4dcf5c19166.jpg" decoding="async" width="1920" height="1080" srcset="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e7/05/14/1110489963_0:66:1201:741_640x0_80_0_0_ac6fe36eb91d47b7852f2bb1d49e702a.jpg 640w,https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e7/05/14/1110489963_0:66:1201:741_1280x0_80_0_0_bbf52c83ef500e1307990d45574a0bca.jpg 1280w,https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e7/05/14/1110489963_0:66:1201:741_1920x0_80_0_0_d30b3fa9dd0bfe34908ce4dcf5c19166.jpg 1920w" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></div></div><div class="media__copyright " data-nosnippet=""><div class="media__copyright-item m-copyright"> © 照片：推特 / @TheBaseLeg </div></div></div></div><div class="article__messengers"><div class="flex-align_center"><span class="article__google-news__label"></span></div><div class="flex-align_center"></div><div class="article__telegram-news flex-align_center"><span class="article__google-news__label">订阅</span></div><div class="flex-align_center"><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://t.me/SputnikInt" title="国际的" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">国际的</a></div><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://telegram.me/sputniknewsindia" title="印度" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">印度</a></div><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://t.me/sputnik_africa" title="非洲" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">非洲</a></div></div></div><div class="article__author"><div class="article__author-item"><div class="article__author-wrapper"><div class="article__author-info"><div class="article__author-name">伊利亚楚卡诺夫</div><div class="article__author-links"> <a class="m-color-main" href="https://sputniknews.com/author_tsukanov_ilya/" title="所有材料">所有材料</a> <a data-modal-open="feedback_author" href="mailto:i.tsukanov@sputniknews.com" title="写给作者">写给作者</a></div></div></div></div></div><div class="article__announce-text">在过去的十五年里，中国在无人机作战能力方面取得了巨大进步，利用了该国庞大的工业基础和本土国防电子产品的重大进步。 </div></div><div class="article__body"><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">一家私人地球成像公司拍下了一张美国国防媒体<a href="https://www.defensenews.com/unmanned/2023/05/18/satellite-image-shows-wz-8-supersonic-drone-at-chinese-base/" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener">推测的</a>照片，照片显示一架中国 WZ-8 火箭动力间谍无人机停在上海以西约 500 公里的六安空军基地的机库外。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">这种三角形的无人机通常从中国人民解放军空军的 H-6K 和 H-6M 战略轰炸机上发射，一直令五角大楼的规划人员感到震惊，美国国家地理空间情报局最近泄露了一份内部评估报告得出的结论是，这些无人机<a href="https://www.navalnews.com/naval-news/2023/04/leaked-us-intel-suggests-first-chinese-wz-8-drone-unit-established/" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener">“几乎可以肯定”</a>已经在 PLAAF 服役。 </div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="media"><div class="article__media"><div class="media" data-media-tipe="photo"><div class="media__size"><div class="photoview__open" data-photoview-group="1110489362" data-photoview-src="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e7/05/14/1110490174_0:0:560:584_1440x900_80_0_1_4bfeaf47fd33f1deb173e2f25b8742e8.png?source-sid=not_sputnik_photo" data-photoview-image-id="1110490156" data-photoview-sharelink="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230520/stealthy-chinese-hypersonic-spy-drone-purportedly-spotted-in-satellite-snap-1110489362.html?share-img=1110490156"><noindex><div class="photoview__open-info"> <span class="photoview__copyright">© Photo : Twitter / @TheBaseLeg</span><span class="photoview__desc-text">对中国六安军事基地的 WZ-8 无人机的分析。</span> </div></noindex><img media-type="photo" data-source-sid="not_sputnik_photo" alt="Analysis of what appears to be a WZ-8 drone at a military airbase in Lu'an, China. - Sputnik International, 1920, 20.05.2023" title="对中国六安军事基地的 WZ-8 无人机的分析。" class="m-vertical lazyload" src="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e7/05/14/1110490174_0:0:560:584_1920x0_80_0_0_72190e03eb4567f6eaad048bf470a071.png" srcset="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=%22http://www.w3.org/2000/svg%22%20width=%221920%22%20height=%222002%22%3E%3C/svg%3E 100w" decoding="async" width="1920" height="2002" data-srcset="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e7/05/14/1110490174_0:0:560:584_640x0_80_0_0_fa8342b115fe2d30b023d574d4168c51.png 640w,https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e7/05/14/1110490174_0:0:560:584_1280x0_80_0_0_780d8e30621b401309b3171ef1adf848.png 1280w,https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e7/05/14/1110490174_0:0:560:584_1920x0_80_0_0_72190e03eb4567f6eaad048bf470a071.png 1920w" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></div></div><div class="media__description " data-nosnippet="">对中国六安军事基地的 WZ-8 无人机的分析。 </div><div class="media__copyright " data-nosnippet=""><div class="media__copyright-item m-copyright"> © 照片：推特 / @TheBaseLeg </div></div></div></div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text"> <a href="https://militarywatchmagazine.com/article/china-worlds-only-hypersonic-aircraft" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener">据报道</a>，这款时尚的无人机配备了双推力发动机，能够加速到高达 7 马赫（每小时 8,350 公里）的速度，并能达到高达<a href="https://www.republicworld.com/world-news/rest-of-the-world-news/china-to-deploy-supersonic-wz-8-jet-propelled-drones-for-surveillance-ops-leaked-papers-articleshow.html" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener">50 公里</a>的高度，从而可以在广阔的地理区域进行实时情报收集。在时间敏感的情况下接近空间。无人机由中国航空工业集团公司生产，利用机载合成孔径雷达系统和光电传感器执行任务，在提供敌方目标高分辨率图像的同时，以高速和高速度快速飞越戒备森严的地区。海拔太高，无法采取应对措施。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text"> WZ-8 于 2019 年在北京的阅兵式上首次公开亮相，其模型出现在 2021 年和 2022 年的航展上。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">关于无人机的大量信息仍处于保密状态，其射程特征未知（其母舰 H-6 的射程在 6,000 到 8,100 公里之间）。据<a href="https://gagadget.com/en/weapons/236877-china-will-use-the-wz-8-supersonic-drone-which-can-reach-speeds-of-3700kmh-and-destroy-aircraft-carriers-f-35-and/" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener">推测</a>，这些无人机可以配备武器，使它们能够与敌方地面、空中和海军部队交战，包括航母群和战斗机。但是，此信息尚未得到独立验证。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">美国国防观察人士<a href="https://www.washingtonpost.com/world/2023/04/18/china-supersonic-drone-taiwan-leaks/" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener">担心</a>，新型无人机极大地增强了中国监视整个印太地区的能力，并且没有提供对抗先进无人机的解决方案。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">中华人民共和国近年来对军队进行了大规模投资，目前该国的军事预算总额位居第二，仅次于美国（分别为 2700 亿美元和 7680 亿美元）。然而，与华盛顿不同的是，北京并未将其军事能力扩展到海外，只在非洲吉布提维持一个军事基地，以方便其参与国际反海盗任务。美国花费了数十年的时间和数十亿美元，试图<a href="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230216/why-is-the-us-militarizing-the-philippines-1107506192.html" target="_blank">在其本国海域内对中国进行军事限制</a>，扩大地区联盟并寻找新的地方来部署先进的新型导弹系统。中国对美国的这些活动进行了猛烈抨击，并呼吁华盛顿停止插手地区事务和企图开启全球军备竞赛。</div></div></div> ]]>;</description><pubDate> Sat, 20 May 2023 17:39:38 GMT</pubDate><guid ispermalink="false"> https://sputniknews.com/20230520/stealthy-chinese-hypersonic-spy-drone-purportedly-spotted-in-satellite-snap-1110489362.html</guid><link/> https://sputniknews.com/20230520/stealthy-chinese-hypersonic-spy-drone-purportedly-spotted-in-satellite-snap-1110489362.html<category>军队</category><category>中国空军</category><category>中国航空工业集团公司 (AVIC)</category><category>中国</category><category>华盛顿</category><category>五角大楼</category><category>无人机</category><category>无人驾驶的航空机</category><category>侦察飞行</category><category>侦察</category></item><item><title><![CDATA[Scott Ritter: How Americans Fell for Washington’s ‘War Racket’]]></title><description><![CDATA[<div class="article__header"><div class="article__announce"><div class="media" data-media-tipe="ar16x9"><div class="media__size"><div class="photoview__open" data-photoview-group="1110476563" data-photoview-src="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/102545/92/1025459225_0:0:2144:1424_1440x900_80_0_1_10b978f4b23fb74a68ef7e12ce49ccac.jpg?source-sid=flickr" data-photoview-image-id="1025459224" data-photoview-sharelink="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230520/scott-ritter-how-americans-fell-for-washingtons-war-racket-1110476563.html?share-img=1025459224"><noindex><div class="photoview__open-info"> <span class="photoview__copyright">© Flickr / <a href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/imcomkorea/" title="晨静周报安装">Morning Calm Weekly Newspaper Installation</a></span><span class="photoview__desc-text">作为美国陆军 (USA) UH-60A 黑鹰 (Blackhawk) 直升机的美国国旗贴片特写</span></div></noindex><img media-type="ar16x9" data-source-sid="flickr" alt="Close-up of a US Flag patch as a US Army (USA) UH-60A Black Hawk (Blackhawk) helicopter  - Sputnik International, 1920, 20.05.2023" title="美国陆军 (USA) UH-60A 黑鹰 (Blackhawk) 直升机的美国国旗补丁特写" src="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/102545/92/1025459225_0:0:2144:1207_1920x0_80_0_0_f3a1bab9ec078adbbb266ae1b3f2eab1.jpg" decoding="async" width="1920" height="1080" srcset="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/102545/92/1025459225_0:0:2144:1207_640x0_80_0_0_6f2d709900d4ec13a219d793d7eba109.jpg 640w,https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/102545/92/1025459225_0:0:2144:1207_1280x0_80_0_0_cd4390ad0c68c207a613220a10ad6a17.jpg 1280w,https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/102545/92/1025459225_0:0:2144:1207_1920x0_80_0_0_f3a1bab9ec078adbbb266ae1b3f2eab1.jpg 1920w" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></div></div><div class="media__copyright " data-nosnippet=""><div class="media__copyright-item m-copyright"> © Flickr / <a href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/imcomkorea/" title="晨静周报安装">Morning Calm 每周报纸安装</a></div></div></div></div><div class="article__messengers"><div class="flex-align_center"><span class="article__google-news__label"></span></div><div class="flex-align_center"></div><div class="article__telegram-news flex-align_center"><span class="article__google-news__label">订阅</span></div><div class="flex-align_center"><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://t.me/SputnikInt" title="国际的" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">国际的</a></div><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://telegram.me/sputniknewsindia" title="印度" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">印度</a></div><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://t.me/sputnik_africa" title="非洲" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">非洲</a></div></div></div><div class="article__author"><div class="article__author-item"><div class="article__author-wrapper"><div class="article__author-image"><img media-type="ar1x1" data-source-sid="not_sputnik_photo" alt=" - Sputnik International" title="" src="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e6/0c/17/1105733958_0:0:334:334_100x100_80_0_0_b457e4e9c850ef224b0cc79059bb38df.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></div><div class="article__author-info"><div class="article__author-name">斯科特·里特</div><div class="article__author-biography">专栏作家</div><div class="article__author-links"><a class="m-color-main" href="https://sputniknews.com/author_ritter_scott/" title="所有材料">所有材料</a></div></div></div></div></div><div class="article__announce-text">史沫特莱·巴特勒 (Smedley Butler) 曾两次获得国会荣誉勋章，曾任美国海军陆战队少将，他曾说过一句著名的话：“战争是一场喧嚣”。 </div></div><div class="article__body"><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">谈到他为国家服务的 33 年，巴特勒指出，他“大部分时间都在为大企业、华尔街和银行家做一名高级肌肉男。简而言之，我是一个敲诈勒索者，一个资本主义的流氓。”</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">不幸的是，巴特勒的话，反映了他在 1900 年代初期的服务，在今天也引起了共鸣。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">它不必是这样的。后越战时代，尤其是在罗纳德·里根总统的领导下，美国开始重新爱上<a href="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230321/us-invasion-of-iraq-helped-bolster-chinese-iranian-influence-in-middle-east-experts-say-1108629155.html" target="_blank">军队</a>。那些服役的人有一种自豪感，一种逐渐被美国公众接受的爱国责任感。 1990 年 5 月，我参加了在华盛顿特区举行的武装服务周活动，在武装服务日之前，我在首都购物中心举办了一场展览，介绍现场检查机构在解除美国和美国核武库方面的工作和苏联。数百名前来了解我们工作的人真正感兴趣。 1991 年 5 月，随着美国在<a href="https://sputnikglobe.com/20210218/study-claims-sarin-and-pesticides-not-depleted-uranium-most-likely-causes-of-gulf-war-syndrome-1082118092.html" target="_blank">海湾战争</a>中取得成功（我参与其中），爱国主义达到了历史最高点，武装部队日庆祝活动似乎反映了对服役人员的真正尊重和钦佩由他们表面上捍卫的人。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">但没有什么是永恒的——正如电影《角斗士》中的一句话敏锐地观察到的那样，“暴民是善变的。”只要角斗士能站在斗兽场的中央，对着人群大喊：“你们不觉得有趣吗？”他将在社会上占有一席之地。但是一旦角斗士对他“招待”的人的心理造成不便，人群就会变得不高兴，角斗士很容易被遗忘。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text"> 1991 年的海湾战争是一场轻松的娱乐活动——军事力量的大规模展示，一个被彻底击败、容易识别的敌人，所有这些都以极低的生命代价——154 人死亡。这些男男女女为之献出生命的事业——解放<a href="https://sputnikglobe.com/20221126/kuwait-reports-first-cholera-case-1104710289.html" target="_blank">科威特</a>——很快就被遗忘了，因为美国卷入了长达数十年的推翻<a href="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230329/us-senate-passes-bill-to-repeal-1991-2002-iraq-war-authorizations-1108932456.html" target="_blank">伊拉克</a>总统萨达姆侯赛因的努力。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text"> <a href="https://sputnikglobe.com/20220912/democrats-mark-september-11-anniversary-by-comparing-capitol-rioters-to-911-hijackers-1100660758.html" target="_blank">9/11</a>的可怕事件让美国人再次团结在那些在武装部队服役的人周围。在美国遭受恐怖袭击之后，整个国家都指望那些穿制服的男男女女将他们从一个很少有人能认出来，甚至更少人能理解的敌人手中解救出来。然而，这种盲目相信政府会使用武装部队来实现美国人民认同的事业，却被政府中的那些人破坏了，他们滥用这种爱国热情的复兴来与萨达姆侯赛因算账，将资源从主要任务中转移出来。打败袭击美国的全球恐怖势力，反而卷入以伪造情报为基础的非法侵略战争，其目的与提升美国地缘政治实力无关，与保护美国无关。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">看来，战争终究是一场喧嚣。 20 多年过去了，美国一直在努力界定它与身穿美国军队制服的人的关系。 2021 年 8 月，美国军队从<a href="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230320/us-seeks-to-control-oil-rich-iraq-even-20-years-after-invasion-russian-ambassador-1108609105.html" target="_blank">阿富汗</a>喀布尔仓促<a href="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230506/us-created-toxic-cancerous-new-police--security-forces-in-afghanistan---former-envoy-1110131532.html" target="_blank">撤出</a>，全球反恐斗争已经消散，得出了可耻的结论。今天，美国正面临着两个全球大国，即俄罗斯（在乌克兰）和中国（在台湾） ).大国冲突的范围和规模，用欧洲盟军最高指挥官美国将军克里斯托弗·卡沃利的话来说，“超出了大多数美国人的想象”。 20 年的低强度冲突使大多数美国人习惯于将冲突视为视频游戏，真人版的“使命召唤”，其中死亡被最小化为数字娱乐。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">乌克兰的<a href="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230517/does-poland-want-zelensky-to-quit-natos-proxy-war-as-sy-hersh-claims-1110421488.html" target="_blank">代理人战争</a>表明这是一个谎言，那些直接了解战争的人总是承认它是谎言。数十万人死亡，数千万人流离失所，数万亿美元的资源丢失或被毁——所有这一切都发生在一年多一点的时间里。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">在美国庆祝武装部队日之际，人们希望那些我们表面上尊敬的人在与俄罗斯或中国发生冲突时所付出的牺牲将在美国人民的脑海中留下沉重的负担。美国军人的任务是捍卫可恶的乌克兰新纳粹政权，还是在<a href="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230519/us-taiwan-clinch-21st-century-trade-pact-deal-amid-washington-beijing-tensions-1110454865.html" target="_blank">台独</a>问题上挑衅中国？美国注定要成为世界警察吗？如果是，我们正在执行哪些法律？联合国宪章？或者我们自己的“基于规则的国际秩序”，经过更仔细的审查，它与史沫特莱·巴特勒 (Smedley Butler) 多年前敏锐地警告过的系统差不多。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">美国的战争风格已经变得只不过是敲诈勒索，而起诉它的人就是敲诈勒索。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">这不是哈里杜鲁门总统在 1949 年设立武装部队日时所设想的武装部队与美国公民之间的关系。我们人民应该好好反思目前的状况，并采取纠正行动，在我们永远失去假期的初衷之前。</div></div></div> ]]>;</description><pubDate> Sat, 20 May 2023 16:00:00 GMT</pubDate><guid ispermalink="false"> https://sputniknews.com/20230520/scott-ritter-how-americans-fell-for-washingtons-war-racket-1110476563.html</guid><link/> https://sputniknews.com/20230520/scott-ritter-how-americans-fell-for-washingtons-war-racket-1110476563.html<category>分析</category><category>我们</category><category>乌克兰</category><category>中国</category><category>华盛顿</category><category>海湾战争</category></item></channel></rss>